{"tid":1459651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[機埸文宣] 對遊客宣揚警察假扮示威者製造衝突","createTime":"2019-08-12T18:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T08:52:08.000Z","uid":14480,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"db3eb9c472d1522c76ffbf3c8eef862d040df100","tid":1459651,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:47:23.000Z","msg":"今日去到機埸，大家都係講緊Dun trust hk police同埋還眼<br />\n我明白大家都好嬲811發生既所有事<br />\n但係如果政府唔可以係機埸強硬清埸，<br />\n就肯定又會出動臥底扮示威者<br />\n而最大機會係扮示威者衝突持反對意見既&quot;遊客&quot;<br />\n當然，示威者可以係差佬扮，遊客都可以係公安扮<br />\n上演一場完美既中港衝突，然後係暴區入面班防暴就可以出黎清場喇<br />\n<br />\n為左廢左政府呢一步可用之棋，<br />\n希望各位手足，黎緊係機場要即刻瘋狂宣揚呢樣野，<br />\n咁樣可以長塞長有，亦都保護返在場手足。<br />\n<br />\n各位點睇？<br />\n我朋友今日比黃絲暴徒搞到黎唔到香港接唔到機，<br />\n我聽日又要再去接機！"},{"pid":"c322c0be2fb752af3416257f85a36c3077921e21","tid":1459651,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:48:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ee48c866a3c46e416d259f0d477c51e736ec850","tid":1459651,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:48:30.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"b7509dfcba486fd56ac9cf255ecf3cd4211f331d","tid":1459651,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:56:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"887ae7704db6c723b51fbe107ede32fa13fc4b47","tid":1459651,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:02:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a8365a442f2cbe9da043e226ab25e396659ff46","tid":1459651,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:02:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94f1c965bae3ffae2e068211b365bcb6caed0b5a","tid":1459651,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:11:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4884f93df1591acd6125feefdbe8716c9bd7c003","tid":1459651,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0